  "text": "Fourth: When the Catalyst of the Mind is processed by the entity the Experience of the Mind results. Is this correct? I am Ra. There are subtle misdirections in this simple statement having to do with the overriding qualities of the Significator. It is so that catalyst yields experience. However, through free will and the faculty of imperfect memory catalyst is most often only partially used and the experience thus correspondingly skewed.",
